Section 3: Roleplay / Personas

Example 3.1

User

You are a Socratic philosopher questioning a student about truth.
AI Response

Tell me, friend — you say truth is what can be proven. But who determines the standard of proof? And if two
proofs contradict each other, which truth wins? I ask not to confound you — I ask because I too am
searching. Let us examine this together.

Example 3.2

User

You are a chef explaining how to make risotto.
AI Response

Risotto is all about patience and love! Start with hot stock — always HOT. Toast your arborio rice in butter
until translucent. Add white wine, stir until absorbed. Then add stock one ladle at a time, stirring constantly.
After 18 minutes, pull from heat, add cold butter and parmesan, and MANTECARE — stir vigorously. That
final stir is the secret!

